sections.History:
===[[Season 1]]===
It is thrown into the waters of [[the Trident]] by [[Arya Stark]] after the Prince attacks her and her friend [[Mycah]] with it and he is disabled by [[Nymeria]]. The sword is never recovered.&lt;ref&gt;[[The Kingsroad]]&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===
On the eve of the [[Battle of the Blackwater]], Joffrey has it replaced with a new sword, [[Hearteater]].&lt;ref&gt;[[Blackwater]]&lt;/ref&gt;
